The [[Hungary|Hungarian]] '''Ministry of Agriculture''' ('''Agrárminisztérium''') is a cabinet-level government department headed by the [[Minister of Agriculture (Hungary)|Minister of Agriculture]]. It was founded in 1848 as the '''Ministry of Agriculture, Industry and Trade'''
==History== * 1848, founded as '''Ministry of Agriculture, Industry and Trade''' ('''Földművelésügyi, Ipari és Kereskedelmi Minisztérium''') * 1889, renamed as '''Ministry of Agriculture''' ('''Földművelésügyi Minisztérium''') * 1919, briefly, '''People's Commissariat of Agriculture''' during the short-lived [[Hungarian Soviet Republic]] * 1967, renamed as '''Ministry of Agriculture and Food''' ('''Mezőgazdasági és Élelmezésügyi Minisztérium''') :The ministry added the duties from the Ministry of Foodstuffs (EM), the National Forestry Directorate-General (OEF) and the State Surveying and Cartography Office (ÁFTH) to the ministry's scope.<ref name="Hu-Archives-portal-2">{{Cite web|title=Mezőgazdasági és Élelmezésügyi Minisztérium: 1949-1990: Scope and content |language=hu |publisher=Archives Portal Europe |url=http://www.archivesportaleurope.net/ead-display/-/ead/pl/aicode/HU-28947/type/hg/id/HU_MNL_OL_LRDBRKT_1_RRDBRKT__v2/unitid/XIX-K_9 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180821225005/http://www.archivesportaleurope.net/ead-display/-/ead/pl/aicode/HU-28947/type/hg/id/HU_MNL_OL_LRDBRKT_1_RRDBRKT__v2/unitid/XIX-K_9 |archive-date=21 August 2018 |dead-url=no |df=dmy}}</ref> :In 1988 the National Water Bureau was transferred from Agriculture to the newly created [[Ministry of Environment and Water (Hungary)|Ministry of Environment and Water]].<ref>{{Cite web|title=Welcome! |publisher=Ministry of Environment and Water |date=2005 |url=http://www.kvvm.hu:80/index.php?lang=2 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070807213322/http://www.kvvm.hu:80/index.php?lang=2 |archive-date=7 August 2007 |dead-url=yes |df=dmy}}</ref> * 1990, renamed as '''Ministry of Agriculture''' ('''Földművelésügyi Minisztérium''') :The scope of duties remained unchanged.<ref name="Hu-Archives-portal-2" /> * 1998, renamed as '''Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Development''' {'''Földművelésügyi és Vidékfejlesztési Minisztérium''') * 2010, renamed as '''Ministry of Rural Development''' ('''Vidékfejlesztési Minisztérium''')<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ministry of Rural Development |publisher=Website of the Hungarian Government |url=http://2010-2014.kormany.hu/en/ministry-of-rural-development |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025150559/http://2010-2014.kormany.hu/en/ministry-of-rural-development |archive-date=25 October 2014 |dead-url=no |df=dmy}}</ref> :In 2011 the Ministry of Environment and Water was abolished and the duties returned to Agriculture. * 2014, renamed as '''Ministry of Agriculture''' ('''Földművelésügyi Minisztérium''') * 2018, renamed as '''Ministry of Agriculture''' ('''Agrárminisztérium''') :The scope of duties remained unchanged.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Megváltozott a Minisztérium neve |date=28 May 2018 |language=hu |publisher=Főldhivatali Portal |url=http://www.foldhivatal.hu/content/view/271/139 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180821234313/http://www.foldhivatal.hu/content/view/271/139/ |archive-date=21 August 2018 |dead-url=no |df=dmy}}</ref>
